<seg id="1">Indonesia upset by reports Australian embassy used as a spy base</seg>
<seg id="2">1 (UPI) -- Indonesian officials said they'd ask the Australian ambassador about reports alleging Australia used its Jakarta embassy to spy on terrorists and politicians.</seg>
<seg id="3">"The conduct as reported was not at all reflecting the spirit of friendly relations" and such activities would be considered "a serious breach of security, which cannot be accepted," the Indonesian Foreign Ministry said Friday.</seg>
