<seg id="7">The pair batted the entire final session and have put on 133 for the third wicket.</seg>
<seg id="8">Bell dominated the Ashes series in England earlier this year, scoring 562 runs at an average of 62.44 to help seal a 3-0 triumph.</seg>
<seg id="9">The 31-year-old was at it again today, taking full advantage of a WA attack missing injured seamer Burt Cockley to make an early statement of intent on tour.</seg>
<seg id="10">Bell crafted 11 fours and smashed two crisp sixes straight down the ground to put him within striking range of a well-deserved ton.</seg>
