<seg id="1">Candy Belle vintage returns with Christmas theme on November 2</seg>
<seg id="2">Despite the calendar only just ticking over to November, organised vintage fans have pulled out all the stops to ensure the fifth Candy Belle Christmas Cracker goes off with a bang.</seg>
<seg id="3">Returning to The Caledonian by Thistle hotel, over 20 stall holders get your Christmas shopping off to a good start with a range of clothing, gifts, homeware and accessories.</seg>
<seg id="4">But what can you expect from the festive themed event?</seg>
<seg id="5">Why not take a look at our highlights...</seg>
<seg id="6">Our top vintage picks</seg>
<seg id="7">Looking for something a little different to a multipack of snowman printed cards to bring good tidings to your friends and family?</seg>
<seg id="8">Then a trip to the Candy Belle vintage photobooth will have you pulling your best cheesy grin that can be printed on postcards for a unique way to mark the holidays.</seg>
<seg id="9">Little ones can ensure their letter to Santa is received nice and early, as Father Christmas will take up residence in the specially decked out grotto from 12pm until 2pm.</seg>
