<seg id="11">It was the club that picked this up from (the blogosphere) and did the rest.</seg>
<seg id="12">If the media has not given PAFC due credit as yet, then I'm doing it for them now.</seg>
<seg id="13">Way left AAMI Stadium on Saturday night - after the Power achieved another remarkable comeback to beat West Coast by five points - saying: "In my head I can see Peter's smile."</seg>
<seg id="14">There are many smiling as several good things continue to unfold at Alberton today, not only on the field and in the front office.</seg>
<seg id="15">The club that was supposedly hurting the image of SA football is making an extraordinary recovery.</seg>
