<seg id="45">This is a step forward for a maturing democracy.</seg>
<seg id="46">We will now press ahead with establishing a Welsh treasury.</seg>
<seg id="47">Powers for a purpose.</seg>
<seg id="48">Borrowing for a purpose.</seg>
<seg id="49">We now need to get on and improve our infrastructure and boost our economy.</seg>
