<seg id="1">Dynamo eliminate Impact from MLS playoffs</seg>
<seg id="2">A grinding end to the regular season resulted in an undisciplined playoff exit for the Montreal Impact.</seg>
<seg id="3">First-half goals by Will Bruin and Oscar Boniek Garcia sucked the life out of the Impact as the Houston Dynamo bounced them from Major League Soccer's post-season with a 3-0 victory on Thursday.</seg>
