<seg id="17">Mr Devereux has since repaid more than $68,000 to the council.</seg>
<seg id="18">Mr Devereux was sentenced to 12 months jail for corruption and six-months jail concurrent for each of four false testimony offences, with one to commence three months before the end of the head sentence.</seg>
