<seg id="16">Jeff Hanneman 1964-2013," posted Megadeth's Dave Mustaine.</seg>
<seg id="17">He is survived by his wife Kathryn, whom he married in 1997, his sister Kathy and his brothers Michael and Larry.</seg>
