<seg id="1">Olomouc opens public ice rink in historical centre</seg>
<seg id="2">The organiser of the Olomouc Christmas markets and ice skating, Pavel Spálený, said that the planned work on the ice rink began on 26 October and from Wednesday ice making machine has been operating.</seg>
<seg id="3">The ice layer is already seven centimetres thick and by Friday morning the surface will be ready for the first visitors.</seg>
