<seg id="7">The streets of Olomouc are already reminiscent of the coming Christmas.</seg>
<seg id="8">Last year, the ice rink was installed directly in front of the main entrance to the town hall on the square Horní Náměstí, due to the repairs on the square Dolní Náměstí.</seg>
