<seg id="32">Zoe's Place Baby Hospice runs respite, palliative and end of life care to families and their children from newborn babies up to five-year-olds who have life-limiting or life-threatening conditions.</seg>
<seg id="33">Called Zoe's because it's the Greek word for 'gift of life', the charity provides the only 'baby-specific' hospices in Britain.</seg>
