<seg id="20">"You've got to re-jig it and we were left with talls and when you've got to keep rotating talls and find spots for them... it doesn't allow you to have the fexlibility when you lose two medium players," he said.</seg>
<seg id="21">Malthouse said Henderson "played well back and he certainly played well forward."</seg>
