<seg id="2">Melbourne artist Vincent Fantauzzo pictured in his Southbank studio, with the painting of his girlfriend, actor Asher Keddie, for the Archibald Prize.</seg>
<seg id="3">Picture: JASON EDWARDS Source: adelaidenow</seg>
<seg id="4">AFTER passing up many requests to sit for the Archibald Prize, acting golden girl Asher Keddie was finally made an offer she couldn't refuse.</seg>
<seg id="5">Her new beau, Melbourne artist Vincent Fantauzzo, has captured the private side of the Offspring and Paper Giants star in a stunning 3m portrait.</seg>
