<seg id="7">"It's beautiful," she said.</seg>
<seg id="8">There's a lot of love and trust in my eyes, and stillness, and it makes me feel happy to look at it.</seg>
<seg id="9">It's a celebration for us, in a way.</seg>
<seg id="10">There's a lot of loveliness in our lives at the moment and this was something we could enjoy doing together and collaborating on.</seg>
